      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! It truly breaks my heart to even think about parting with this beauty, but it's time for her to find a new home where she'll be just as cherished. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always kept indoors, strictly hand-washed, and maintained with an open checkbook. It\u2019s in absolutely breathtaking condition, looking and smelling just like it did on the showroom floor. There\u2019s a microscopic mark on the door sill that you\u2019d need a magnifying glass to find, but that\u2019s just a sign of a car that\u2019s been enjoyed! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s virtually flawless and ready for a weekend cruise, you\u2019ve found it. Let\u2019s chat!",
